  x86 stable, bug #369573

  19 Sep 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -rspec-mocks-2.5.0.ebuild:
  Remove old version.

  14 Sep 2011; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> rspec-mocks-2.6.0.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (bug #369573).

  27 Aug 2011; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> rspec-mocks-2.6.0.ebuild:
  Marked ~x64-macos

  02 Aug 2011; Markos Chandras <hwoarang@gentoo.org> rspec-mocks-2.6.0.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #369573

  23 Jul 2011; Kacper Kowalik <xarthisius@gentoo.org> rspec-mocks-2.6.0.ebuild:
  ppc stable wrt #369573

  31 May 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> rspec-mocks-2.5.0.ebuild:
  Drop ruby19 to create a stable candidate.

  23 May 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> rspec-mocks-2.6.0.ebuild:
  Add jruby support.

  13 May 2011; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org>
  -rspec-mocks-2.0.0_beta22.ebuild, -rspec-mocks-2.4.0.ebuild:
  Remove old versions.

